```r
sinspuPCoAMeta %>%
  group_by(virus.bin,sampleloc) %>%
  summarise(Dim1 = mean(Dim1),
            Dim2 = mean(Dim2)) -> virussamplelocCentroid

ggplot(sinspuPCoAMeta,
       aes(x = Dim1,
           y = Dim2,
           color = virus.bin)) +
  geom_point(size = 2,
             alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_color_manual(name = \Respiratory viral\ninfection status\"
